title: Weak-interaction Route-B standalone audit

closure_gate.rule: combined hard/watch pass requires both CKM and PMNS gates.
closure_gate.next_action: keep watch until CKM first-row primary inputs are updated

ckm_gate.rule: hard if abs(z)<=3, watch if abs(z)<=2 (abs(z)>2 and <=3 => watch)

pmns_gate.reason: PMNS closure is out of scope in this CKM first-row pack.

correlation_reassessment.watch_lock_reason: reported first-row sigma is below watch-pass requirement; input precision update is required.

ckm_gate.watch_lock_reason: reported first-row sigma is below watch-pass requirement; input precision update is required.

pmns_gate.rule: NuFIT v5.2 row-1 3 range proxies; sigma_proxy=(high-low)/6; hard if abs(z)<=3, watch if abs(z)<=2.

notes: B-route standalone gate uses same I/F (Q/logft/CKM/PMNS) while removing Route-A pass dependency.
This pack is a decision baseline for Step 8.7.31; transition target is B_standalone_pass.
